      "content": "is it really that serious? a few hours or even a whole day apart seems like a lot. i've read online that if you just space them out well it's fine. can't i just take the simvastatin right before bed and the clarithromycin in the morning and be good? i really don't want to deal with the hassle of getting a new prescription right now.",
